tip.text: Good place to catch the sunset
Amazing store showcasing  Portuguese products, great packaging and design
Garlic shrimp were the best, followed by Edible Crab and tiger shrimp. Oysters lacked brininess so had no flavor. Arrive before 6pm and expect a 45 min wait, if later, wait can be excessively long
Photogenic but small fish monger, nice to walk around the surrounding streets
